This paper discusses the impact of batch size on active learning for text classification, which is a topic that falls under the intersection of machine learning (cs.LG), natural language processing (cs.CL), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of convolutional neural networks (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques in their experiments. Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
